<NEW>

If GRIMLOCK's last roar was loud, then this one would be considered
deafening as its sound boomed out! While he had no sonic ability
per'se, his brute force to everything, including his roar, made up for
it in spades!

"Why Wheelie attack Grimlock?" He said at first as he wheeled around
temporarily disoriented by WHEELIE's unconventional attack and words.

There was a grunt from SLAG as he spun around as WHEELIE was leaping
off GRIMLOCK, with SNARL and SLUDGE turning as well.

"Me no care!" GRIMLOCK said, his optics darknening as his anger caused
him to loose all vestige of control. "Me Grimlock smash!"

He took off running after WHEELIE, the other DINOBOTS right behind,
follwing him right over the bridge.

As the last DINOBOT crossed SWOOP fired a blast at the logs and the
bridge exploded into fire and smoke, the remains of which fell down
hundreds of feet into the swiftly flowing river below.

GRIMLOCK and the DINOBOTS hardly noticed as they continued to chase WHEELIE!

(TAG)

- Preston
